message.body: When does timateo leave the land of 10000 lakes?
Less than a week... How are you?
I'm doing really well! Just laying around, met up with Sam prince for breakfast and now talking katie - how are u??
I'm ok, feeling stressed. Whats new?! How is she?
She had a really nice weekend of chill time which reminded her of home :)
Like chill with people instead of always "going out"
That's really good to hear. What happened with pranna last night?
What do u mean?
Your tweet?
It was raining really hard so I didn't want to leave lol - I took a pic but it didn't upload. This boy needs more cash so I'm back and now princess is guilting
You're back where? Why is she building
Guilting
Me into taking another weekend off for her to come visit my birthday. Its that typical rigid "this is the only way to celebrate" stirring up feelings lol
Yikes... That's a long ways off though
Are u on muscle relaxers?? I'm back at pranna - its only two weeks away so we have to start planning if one of us is going to visit
You said she wants to visit your birthday?
Her birthday lol
Yea I remember you saying that you were going to do that, that's why I was confused! Yep bring your candles and organic raspberries and specially composed prayers
I think that's the only way.... Can u fly in too?? We forgot to schedule our year around it...
Right and now pig iron is going to get in the way of planning for next year!
Geez marty!!
How are you feeling?
Womp womp - still pretty dizzy
Well actually drink so much water you constantly have to pee. Drink drink drink. It works!
Remember when we had to go to an A.A meeting for health class??? How ISDD 88 get away with that?
Yea, not so anonymous anymore!
Seriously crazy shit!
Feeling better?
SO much better! And I'm cutting alcohol out of the diet missy!!!
Why?!
Otherwise I'm going to die!!! It was so out of hand and I'm sick of feeling lousy
